{"tid":1926303,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地抽夠利記水未？","createTime":"2020-03-15T04:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T08:47:49.000Z","uid":15886,"like":15,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9999cd169252302cb51c68c0f5cd9248e002be","tid":1926303,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"見到你地係咁抽利記水<br />\n我真係越諗越撚灰<br />\n根本唔知自己做乜要支持一隊球隊10幾年而換得俾人嘲笑既地步<br />\n知唔知咩叫尊重、respect?<br />\n好撚煩囉成日搬D歷史出o黎話點話點<br />\n我心諗一句, 你講既我全部知, 甚至乎你唔知既我都知<br />\n第一唔使你教我<br />\n第二唔使你分析我聽<br />\n第三我無屌你隊愛隊先<br />\n一失分出面最少半版post 係抽水<br />\n好難忍到一個都唔reply<br />\n或者轉去其他forum 係唯一解決方法"},{"pid":"5109b8e6a734604240fb53e945c382dbbc53f9e3","tid":1926303,"uid":24519,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"未"},{"pid":"1c8193c0f4969d4ec0b7f5b05df7ac253e5e185b","tid":1926303,"uid":314983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee07b835f64175aacbf6c158c1364971a251626","tid":1926303,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afeb115357a256ab497a059eac2bcb8d66ea9ba7","tid":1926303,"uid":199441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"未"},{"pid":"2594c592bda5c53140746ddc1e727d89d372fbb0","tid":1926303,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"睇黎都係回家 返高登算了"},{"pid":"e21f8448ff4ed61b8e3fd5cafd69350811ec8c0d","tid":1926303,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"考古"},{"pid":"6579d3db5a05131a533378af298b3e63c9412d67","tid":1926303,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2594c592bda5c53